# Agent configuration
# Columns: <agent_name>  <skills_path>  [instruction_symlink]
#
#   skills_path        — where skill symlinks are deployed
#   instruction_symlink — ABSOLUTE path (~ expanded) where the agent reads its
#                         global instruction file. do-stow.sh creates a symlink
#                         there pointing back to AGENTS.md in this repo.
#                         Use - if the agent reads AGENTS.md by walking up from
#                         CWD (e.g. codex reads ~/AGENTS.md automatically).
#
# Cursor has no global instruction file — it reads .cursor/rules/ per-project only.
# When working inside this repo, agents find AGENTS.md in the repo root directly.

claude   ~/.claude/skills   ~/.claude/CLAUDE.md
codex    ~/.codex/skills    ~/AGENTS.md
gemini   ~/.gemini/skills   ~/.gemini/GEMINI.md
cursor   ~/.cursor/rules    -
